  "materials_text": "",
  "steps": [
    "Mix concentrated Euplotes cells together with Ethanol 70% in a ratio of 1:1. Better to have a completely starved Euplotes culture to avoid autofuorescence from bacteria/algae.",
    "Add DAPI (0.01 mg/ml) to the mix in a ratio of 1:10, and stain for 15 minutes at room temperature.",
    "Observe cells by fluorescence microscopy."
